latestIgtvVideos.title: My mother’s upbringing over anything 🥰
latestIgtvVideos.caption: 2 years back when we used to visit protest sites for an appeal we didn’t realise it would teach us numerous things. We met @arfakhanum from @thewirein in one of the protest and had a little chat it’s so beautiful to know we connected on such deep level that she would remember us. This video is also dedicated to Vinod dua who’s guidance and knowledge will always be here with us through tough times. @its_yashmeena my mother is such a fearless women. There’s so much that I’ve already learn from her and there’s so much still left to learn. I love you mumma ❤️
